@namespace url(http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml);

@-moz-document domain("app.nirvanahq.com") {

#east li.view.next {  visibility: hidden; }
#east li.view.next:before {
  visibility: visible;
  content:'This Week'; 
}

#east li.view.focus {  visibility: hidden; }
#east li.view.focus:before {
  visibility: visible;
  content:'Today'; 
}

#east li.view.later {  visibility: hidden; }
#east li.view.later:before {
  visibility: visible;
  content:'Soon'; 
}

#east li.view.someday {  visibility: hidden; }
#east li.view.someday:before {
  visibility: visible;
  content:'Maybe'; 
}

#east li.later {
  background-repeat: no-repeat !important;
  background-position: 23px 4px;
  background-image:url(data:image/png;base64,) !important;
  
}

#east li.next {
  background-repeat: no-repeat !important;
  background-position: 23px 4px;
  background-image:url(data:image/png;base64,) !important;
}  
  
#east li.focus {
  background-repeat: no-repeat !important;
  background-position: 23px 4px;
  background-image:url(data:image/png;base64,) !important;
}
  
#east li.someday {
  background-repeat: no-repeat !important;
  background-position: 23px 4px;
    background-image: url(data:image/png;base64,) !important;
}

}
